{"lemma":"عَوْف","slug":"عَوْف","root":"ع.#.ف","root_slug":"ع-_-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-_-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31034"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D9%81"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31034","headword_ar":"عَوْفٌ","root":"Ewf","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A state, condition,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.) So in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEima Eawofuka","text_ar":"نَعِمَ عَوْفُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May thy state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pleasant"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobaHa fulaAnN biEawofi sawo'K","text_ar":"اَصْبَحَ فُلَانٌ بِعَوْفِ سَوْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biEawofi xayorK","text_ar":"بِعَوْفِ خَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one entered upon the morning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, simply,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in an evil state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a good state:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to some of the lexicologists, one should not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biEawofi xayorK","text_ar":"بِعَوْفِ خَيْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but only"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ar~K","text_ar":"شَرٍّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sawo'K","text_ar":"سَوْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IDrd, O.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fortune;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jad~N","text_ar":"جَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaZ~N","text_ar":"حَظٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K.) And so, accord. to some, in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEima Eawofuka","text_ar":"نَعِمَ عَوْفُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May thy fortune be good"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaAy^irN","text_ar":"طَايِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An omen"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, TA.) And thus it is said to signify in the form of prayer above mentioned: (TA:) [for,] as some say, the meaning is,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEima Tayoruka","text_ar":"نَعِمَ طَيْرُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May thy omen be good"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, TA.) ―         -b4-  And The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*akar","text_ar":"ذَكَر"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K.) One says to a man on the morning after his first going in to his wife,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEima Eawofuka","text_ar":"نَعِمَ عَوْفُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning thereby the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*akar","text_ar":"ذَكَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May thy"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*kr","text_ar":"ذكر"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be in a good state"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, TA.) A'Obeyd says, Some men used to explain ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yataA^aw~alu","text_ar":"يَتَاَوَّلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yatanaAwalu","text_ar":"يَتَنَاوَلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put in the O])"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEawof","text_ar":"العَوْف"},{"kind":"text","text":"as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroj","text_ar":"فَرْج"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*akar","text_ar":"ذَكَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and I mentioned it to AA, and he disapproved it: (S, O, TA:) but a verse has been cited in which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawofiY","text_ar":"عَوْفِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[certainly] means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*akariY","text_ar":"ذَكَرِى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A guest."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O, K.) And thus it has been expl. as used in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEima Eawofuka","text_ar":"نَعِمَ عَوْفُكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, * TA.) ―         -b6-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cock."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) ―         -b7-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"because he seeks his prey (↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yataEaw~afu","text_ar":"يَتَعَوَّفُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":") by night. (O, K.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And The wolf."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) ―         -b9-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who toils,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seeks the means of subsistence, for his household,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"family."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O, K.) ―         -b10-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain idol."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) ―         -b11-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A species of trees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a species of plants,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the plants of the desert,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sweet odour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, O, K.) ―         -b12-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^um~u EawofK","text_ar":"اُمُّ عَوْفٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraAdap","text_ar":"جَرَادَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) [i. e.] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"female of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraAd","text_ar":"جَرَاد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"locust"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abuw EawofK","text_ar":"اَبُو عَوْفٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaraAd","text_ar":"جَرَاد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"male locust"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Az, O, K.)       -A2-  Also (i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawofN","text_ar":"عَوْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a good manner of tending"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasturing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[cattle]: (O, K:) [or rather, simply,] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tending"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasturing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[cattle]: so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu laHasanu","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَحَسَنُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEawofi fiY A_ibilihi","text_ar":"العَوْفِ فِى اـِبِلِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is one who has a good quality of tending,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasturing, in respect of his camels"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","O","AHn","K"]}]}}